Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:02.45,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}弄髒的襯衫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:04.41,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}沾染上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:08.37,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}這自欺欺人的謊言…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.37,0:02:13.50,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,348)}我到底在保護什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:17.92,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}不畏失去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:21.64,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}即便長大成人 也心懷夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:23.64,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}因為我只希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:26.14,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}自己能將這些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:29.06,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,351)}視為驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:33.11,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}吐出來 捨棄掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:34.98,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:36.73,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,347)}回憶起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:38.65,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:43.62,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,980)}希望明天我能這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:53.96,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(363,0)}在這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:58.09,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,519)}毫無改變的街道
